orage
esetroot
gkrellm
gk-volumeplugin
gk-shoot
audacious
universalindentui
icecc
grun
mate-power-applet

install script:
user@home~$
installation icewm si ce nest pasdeja fait:
sudo apt-get install icewm+resource



http://forums.fedoraforum.org/showthread.php?t=282433


